queries.sql: SELECT `al`.*, `u`.`username` as `uploader_name`, `u`.`email` as `uploader_email`, COUNT(ald.id) as recipient_count, COALESCE(SUM(ald.amount), 0) as total_amount FROM `atm_liquidations` `al` LEFT JOIN `users` `u` ON `al`.`uploaded_by` = `u`.`id` LEFT JOIN `atm_liquidation_details` `ald` ON `al`.`id` = `ald`.`atm_liquidation_id` GROUP BY `al`.`id` ORDER BY `al`.`created_at` DESC
